===Kit===
The Switzerland national team's traditional home kit is red shirts, white shorts and red socks, with the away kit being reverse with white shirts, red shorts and white socks, although all-red and all-white kits are not uncommon. Switzerland, since being established in 1895, have always had the same colour code, as tradition and homage to the national colours which are derived from the [[Flag of Switzerland|Swiss flag]]. The current kit manufacturer is [[Puma (brand)|Puma]], who have made their kits since 1998.

